# Chapter 16: Convolutional Neural Networks (CNN)

## Introduction

Convolutional Neural Networks (CNNs) are specialized neural networks designed for image processing tasks.

CNNs automatically learn visual features such as edges, shapes, textures, and objects.

---

# Why CNN?

Traditional Neural Networks struggle with images because of high dimensionality.

CNNs efficiently extract image features.

---

# CNN Architecture

