# CNN vs ANN

| Feature            | ANN    | CNN       |
| ------------------ | ------ | --------- |
| Image Processing   | Poor   | Excellent |
| Parameters         | Large  | Reduced   |
| Feature Extraction | Manual | Automatic |
| Accuracy           | Lower  | Higher    |

